  "risk.subtitle": "Lees zorgvuldig",
  "risk.defaultHtml": "<div class=\"notice-box\"><strong>Important:</strong> TaskMall is a task-based earning platform. Please use the service responsibly and only with funds you can afford to use.</div><h1>1. Tasks & balance</h1><p>Task amounts are deducted from your balance when an order is confirmed. Principal and commission are returned after task completion. Ensure you have sufficient balance and understand the process.</p><h1>2. Withdrawals</h1><p>Withdrawals are subject to platform rules, limits and review. Processing times may vary. You are responsible for providing a correct wallet address.</p><h1>3. No guarantee</h1><p>We do not guarantee any particular returns or outcomes. Task availability and commission rates may change. Use at your own discretion.</p><h1>4. Compliance</h1><p>You must comply with local laws. If your jurisdiction restricts or prohibits such services, do not use TaskMall.</p><h1>5. Contact</h1><p>For questions about risks or processes please contact our customer service.</p>",
